<v Speaker 1>I prefer that they don't stay here.

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:36.440
<v Speaker 1>I prefer that they don't stay here.

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:39.080
<v Speaker 1>I prefer for them not to stay here.

